programme.desc: I have always wanted to try indoor wall climbing. And thanks to Dave Hanson from Colorado Wilderness Rides & Guides and Movement Climbing + Fitness in Boulder, CO, I did just that! And I was the oldest person there. All the other climbers looked like they were straight out of ads or something. Perfect physiques. My palms started sweating just taking in that vista. I am definitely adding indoor climbing to my list of favorite adventure activities. And maybe even someday, taking it outside to the legendary climbing areas of Boulder, CO.
